{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"4bbd4aec05","title":"给张澜、黄炎培的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"872a5c5ccd","index":0,"year":1953,"month":5,"day":13,"articleId":"4bbd4aec05"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji33","name":"毛泽东全集第33卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/33-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji33":{"comments":[{"id":"7521f84f27","publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"4bbd4aec05","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"张澜，当时任中国民主同盟中央委员会主席、中央人民政府副主席。黄炎培，当时任中国民主建国会主任委员、政务院副总理。"},{"id":"381cadc41c","publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"4bbd4aec05","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指张澜、黄炎培1953年5月5日给毛泽东、周恩来的信。信中说：“周孝怀君从上海来信，大意是：希望政府考虑明令三反五反总结束，安感受宽，释放无问题被拘者，扭转人心。附笔还谈到农业税等问题。我们会商一下，认为这些都在政府慎重处理之中，孝怀此函，自是一片忠爱热诚的流露，将原送陈，以供参考。"},{"id":"19f29f8ac5","publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"4bbd4aec05","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"周孝怀，当时任上海民生轮船公司董事长。"}],"contents":[{"id":"b6cd3bc37d","type":"title","text":"给张澜、黄炎培的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"4bbd4aec05"},{"id":"7521f84f27","type":"paragraph","text":"张副主席、黄副总理：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"4bbd4aec05"},{"id":"381cadc41c","type":"paragraph","text":"五月五日惠书及周孝怀先生意见书，收到，阅悉；并已转付有关各部门负责同志阅看。其中有些问题，已请周总理的处。便时尚希转告孝怀先生。此复","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"4bbd4aec05"},{"id":"19f29f8ac5","type":"paragraph","text":"顺致敬意","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"4bbd4aec05"},{"id":"d3a3928d84","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"4bbd4aec05"},{"id":"a694496c0b","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五三年五月十三日","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"4bbd4aec05"},{"id":"06aa2aed1e","type":"paragraph","text":"周书奉还。","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"4bbd4aec05"}],"page":{"id":"d29afe8389","publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"4bbd4aec05","start":167,"end":167}}}},"__N_SSG":true}